            "<p>Other patients don’t like what they see but are ignorant of their right to go elsewhere.</p>",
            "<p>But Prowne himself is not concerned.</p>",
            "<p>But other will take their place, he thought.</p>",
            "<p>These hands are steady enough, but they are large.</p>"
