          "id": 250,
          "question": "<p><a name=\"4979\"></a><div itemprop=\"text\"><p>After sometimes, the faculty members who were involved in all the three tasks were asked to withdraw from one task. As a result, one of the faculty members each opted out of teaching and research, while remaining ones involved in all the three tasks opted out of training. Which one of the following statements, then necessarily follows:</p>\n\n</div><br><br><b>English Language: CAT 2010 | Question: 55</b></p>",
