            "<p>Military power—colonialism—restructuring—feudalism—capitalism</p>",
            "<p>Military power—arrogance—laboratory—modernity—capitalism</p>",
            "<p>Colonial policy—Enlightenment—external modernity—subjection—underdevelopment</p>"
