          "explanation": "<p><a href=\"https://aptitude.gateoverflow.in/8544/cat-2021-set-verbal-ability-reading-comprehension-question\" target=\"_blank\">https://aptitude.gateoverflow.in/8544/cat-2021-set-verbal-ability-reading-comprehension-question</a></p>"
